{"tid":2182092,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如果龍門要攞到金球獎既條件係咩？","createTime":"2020-08-31T05:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T08:38:40.000Z","uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb68014f0e38d1d1c590437c47d2951c2a3ef22","tid":2182092,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"先天條件<br />\n嗰季既前鋒同中場嘅進攻數據唔算最火爆<br />\n例如最勁既前鋒埋單都係喺聯賽入廿幾球<br />\n中場入波同助攻唔算特別多<br />\n而個keeper踢大球會<br />\n<br />\n後天條件<br />\n龍門隊波本身拎到大賽冠軍 <br />\neg.歐聯/四大聯賽冠軍其中一個 最好西甲/英超<br />\n<br />\n最核心條件<br />\n聯賽加歐聯有一半到七成賽事保持不失球<br />\n而全季失波唔過廿球<br />\n<br />\n做到咁樣可唔可以令一個龍門拎到金球獎呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果咁都唔得<br />\n係咪代表龍門永遠都係喺足球世界比人睇低一線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062760a67f16c852448f685dc082abd3a3e15b97","tid":2182092,"uid":32051,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"弱旅出強龍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22294a5bef5a8aeb21bd8c8c7fb7f8b9999829c","tid":2182092,"uid":146267,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"拎世界盃亞軍"},{"pid":"596606ffa17d517e38c74c28f59328601d228e1c","tid":2182092,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:40:47.000Z","msg":"Clean Sheet + 神救 ＋隊波捧到杯"},{"pid":"e0a5a2246ffeee61e017b198a57652883727b27a","tid":2182092,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:43:16.000Z","msg":"世界盃最後互射十二碼幫國家隊拎冠軍🏆。"},{"pid":"85a42e18fe4e0be54eeaa265c708433deebce15a","tid":2182092,"uid":211003,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"龍門要表演即係你防守廢到仆街<br />\n防守廢到仆街又冇咩可能做到勁旅<br />\n當你進攻好撚勁既時候又會俾前鋒搶哂光環<br />\n所以冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad716e7d0fb7f681e1a78e9b2331c92527557a0","tid":2182092,"uid":9150,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"入球或助攻達到雙位數字，<br />\n救出險球/十二碼間接令球隊拿三冠王，<br />\n帶領國家隊係盃賽賽事一球不失。<br />\n呢上呢幾樣係基本"},{"pid":"8daa592d8cbfd3769031e9adb48f02e06bf4db17","tid":2182092,"uid":8733,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"85a42e18fe4e0be54eeaa265c708433deebce15a","tid":2182092,"uid":211003,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"龍門要表演即係你防守廢到仆街<br />\n防守廢到仆街又冇咩可能做到勁旅<br />\n當你進攻好撚勁既時候又會俾前鋒搶哂光環<br />\n所以冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:45:50.000Z","msg":"下體算唔算特別例子"},{"pid":"da7e784a8e8f3a67b9e7194a1dd35c7f625cc4cb","tid":2182092,"uid":116614,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"自己帶波扭11個?"},{"pid":"2a39fdd2e1b68880c4dbfff74bd0eea81f3e2901","tid":2182092,"uid":158145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:47:57.000Z","msg":"神射手<br />\n最多助攻<br />\n撲救成功率100%<br />\n世界盃冠軍<br />\n聯賽冠軍<br />\n歐聯冠軍"},{"pid":"847e66010579b0c96dc6d2a649253e3e341babd6","tid":2182092,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍門要表演即係你防守廢到仆街<br />\n防守廢到仆街又冇咩可能做到勁旅<br />\n<span class=\"red\">當你進攻好撚勁既時候又會俾前鋒搶哂光環</span><br />\n所以冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果好似利記上季果種入波分散晒無一個球員特別多入波又點計"},{"pid":"39da6e2b4e3e6689169ae09db6c5d2a4ed477c2f","tid":2182092,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:49:55.000Z","msg":"唔睇tvb點拎金球獎"},{"pid":"b963c6853b88f669d286f823fd7d44c01120327e","tid":2182092,"uid":211003,"